    "excerpt": "Commercial financing rates in the UK span a wide range depending on product type, lender appetite, and borrower profile — from around 6.5% p.a. for a standard commercial mortgage to 12%+ p.a. for specialist development finance. This guide breaks down current rate benchmarks, the factors lenders use to price deals, and the true cost of commercial borrowing beyond the headline rate.",
