    "metaTitle": "Cost of Bridging Finance: Rates & Fees (2026)",
    "metaDescription": "Full cost of bridging finance explained: monthly interest rates, arrangement fees, valuation and legal charges. Expert guide for UK property developers.",
    "excerpt": "The cost of bridging finance is not a single number — it is the sum of monthly interest, arrangement fees, valuation charges, legal costs, and sometimes an exit fee. Understanding every component is the only way to assess whether a bridging loan stacks up for your project.",
