    "metaDescription": "Explore every option for finance for buying land in the UK — bridging loans, development finance, and land mortgages. Rates, LTVs, and how to apply explained.",
    "excerpt": "Securing finance for buying land is more complex than a standard mortgage, with lenders weighing planning status, intended use, and your exit strategy. This guide explains every option available to UK property developers and investors, from bridging loans to development finance.",
    "category": "general",
    "readingTime": "9 min read",
    "datePublished": "2026-04-19",
