          "For large bridging loans where the exit is a development finance facility (i.e., the bridge is used to acquire land and the development loan will follow post-planning), lenders will want to understand the planning strategy and the intended development finance terms. Our guide to <a href=\"/guides/development-finance-vs-bridging-loans\">development finance vs bridging loans</a> covers the transition between the two products in detail."
